Random notes on the stroop task

What if someone's color blind in the stroop task test - most likely subject is excluded from study
How much of language fluency or proficiency is important for the task? 

Font type, size, viewing distance are all parameters that matter
Left handed/right handed may matter
covariates (e.g., IQ, education, medication)

Other references:
